  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Main objective: To study and validate a questionnaire measuring treatment adherence in
      patients with Hepatitis C virus (HCV) infection.

      Design of the study: Multicentric, prospective, epidemiological study in the field of usual
      clinical practice.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
